Author: CATrashanator
Text: Yeah. I went from, “I’ll be happy at x weight” to “ok. Actually. I’ll be happy at x minus 30 pounds.”

Author: sickcupcake
Text: “I’ll feel so skinny and happy at 105 pounds!” *hits 105* “Oh my god I’m still fucking disgusting. Better lose another 10.”  never enough. I’ve lost like 40 pounds and swear I look the exact same, even though I’ve dropped several sizes and am aware that technically I’m smaller.
